<template>
  <v-container>
    <v-form>
      <v-text-field v-model="address.street" label="Rua" outlined dense></v-text-field>
      <v-text-field v-model="address.city" label="Cidade" outlined dense></v-text-field>
      <v-text-field v-model="address.state" label="Estado" outlined dense></v-text-field>
      <v-btn color="success" @click="submitAddress">Salvar Endereço</v-btn>
    </v-form>
  </v-container>
</template>

<script>
import axios from 'axios';

export default {
  props: {
    registrationId: {
      type: Number,
      required: true,
    },
  },
  data() {
    return {
      address: {
        street: '',
        city: '',
        state: '',
      },
    };
  },
  methods: {
    submitAddress() {
      axios.post('/addresses', { ...this.address, registration_id: this.registrationId })
        .then(() => {
          this.$router.push({ name: 'SearchPage' });
          this.$emit('update');
        })
        .catch(error => {
          console.error('Erro ao adicionar endereço:', error.response.data.message);
        });
    },
  },
}
</script>
